# Verde Mar — Mock API Responses

Documento con los JSON de respuesta para cada endpoint mock en Azure API Management.

---

## AUTH

### POST /api/auth/login

**Request:**
```json
{
    "email": "carlos@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}
```

**Response (200):**
```json
{
    "data": {
        "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.mock-token-verde-mar",
        "user": {
            "id": "usr-001",
            "name": "Carlos Ramírez",
            "email": "carlos@example.com",
            "role": "user",
            "avatar": "https://i.pravatar.cc/150?u=carlos"
        }
    },
    "message": "Inicio de sesión exitoso"
}
```

**Response (401):**
```json
{
    "message": "Credenciales inválidas",
    "status": 401
}
```

---

### POST /api/auth/register

**Request:**
```json
{
    "name": "María López",
    "email": "maria@example.com",
    "password": "securePass456",
    "confirmPassword": "securePass456"
}
```

**Response (201):**
```json
{
    "data": {
        "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.mock-token-new-user",
        "user": {
            "id": "usr-007",
            "name": "María López",
            "email": "maria@example.com",
            "role": "user",
            "avatar": null
        }
    },
    "message": "Registro exitoso"
}
```

**Response (409):**
```json
{
    "message": "El correo electrónico ya está registrado",
    "status": 409
}
```

---

